title: "Gizmos n' Gadgets" (w/ Jacqueline Novak)
itunes:title: "Gizmos n' Gadgets" (w/ Jacqueline Novak)
description:
This week's episode branches into an astonishing amount of cultural topics, much like the linktree of today's special guest, the amazing Jacqueline Novak!

If you want an episode that segues from chicken bones into The Lovely Bones, then look no further. This is the one! But not only that, also: The art of personal branding, the proper way to eat a Buffalo Wing, the end of the line (sexually), horrific turbulence, Grease 2, Matt's skydiving story, proper theater etiquette, and yes...more!
